Adrenaline surged through Leo, eclipsing the fear. "K-V! Data refraction protocol! Now! Night Owl logic! Target instability core! Isolate and amplify embedded non-standard data packets!"\
Executing modified data refraction protocol. High risk of signal degradation and feedback loop. Proceeding! K-V rerouted processing power, its normally calm optical sensor glowing brighter.\
The chaotic static on the main display wavered, then resolved, flickeringly, into the grainy image: Crumbling concrete under a harsh, unfamiliar blue sky. Buildings like skeletons picked clean. Desolation.\
