Source unidentified. Non-standard encoding protocols detected. Signal characteristics inconsistent with known network topography. Multiple analogous feeds detected. The screen split \'96 more ruins, different angles, all bleak, decayed. Then, one feed shifted \'96 a low angle, moving smoothly. Forest. A clearing. Log cabins. People moving, 
