Cryptic. Unhelpful technically. But it confirmed others suspected signals, origins beyond simple system error. He wasn't alone in his core suspicion, even if their methods were vastly different. The knowledge was cold comfort. The problem was vast, complex, and the official channels remained silent. The burden of finding real answers felt heavier than ever.\

\f1\b Scene 14: First Contact
