\f0\i0  But her feet felt rooted to the floor. It wasn't advancing. It wasn't threatening. It was just\'85 there.\
The synthesized voice was quiet, calm, startlingly clear in the small space. "Greetings. I am designated Seeker 03255202. I require technical assistance for critical system failures."\
