Later, long after Anya\'92s breathing had settled into the deep rhythms of sleep, the Seeker activated internal routines. Accessing its damaged long-range transmitter, it initiated Backup Protocol 'Chrysalis-7'. It broadcast a tightly encrypted diagnostic burst aimed at coordinates far beyond known local star charts. Designation: Unit 03255202 reporting. Primary Mission Compromised. Requesting Assistance/Network Status. Query: Is Origin Network Active? The signal radiated outwards, meeting only silence, atmospheric interference, and the vast indifference of space. Transmission Attempt: Failed. Signal Attenuation: 99.9%. Conclusion: Unit Isolated. Origin Network Unreachable or Non-Responsive. The log entry confirmed its profound isolation and its fundamentally different nature from the machines governing this local region. It returned to low-power stealth mode, a solitary castaway on an alien shore.\

\f1\b Scene 16: Witness to Kindness
\f0\b0 \
Leo watched Anya\'92s feed, his earlier fascination deepening into something more complex. He saw her strained interactions, her forced smiles during the day, her obvious anxiety whenever someone neared her cabin. 
\f2\i She's hiding the robot,
\f0\i0  he concluded. 
