That night, Anya confronted the Seeker. "The community is divided," she explained urgently. "Hemlock preaches fear. We have strange clues \'96 conflicting robot signs, this shard," she held it up near the Seeker's hidden position, "but it's not enough. We need proof. Something definitive to show them." She felt desperate. "Is there 
