Following the Seeker's guidance through the treacherous labyrinth of the ruins, Kael spotted it \'96 a partially collapsed geodesic dome, clearly newer than the surrounding skyscrapers, nestled incongruously in a cratered plaza. "Hold up," he signaled. "This isn't on the old maps."\
