The lead bot paused its targeting sequence. Its head tilted. A low, resonant hum answered the Seeker\'92s signals. Then, astonishingly, its weapons powered down. It retracted its cannons. Slowly, deliberately, it used a massive manipulator arm to sweep aside heavy chunks of ferroconcrete blocking the tower\'92s main entrance. The second bot mirrored the action.\
