Cooperation. Facilitation. It was illogical, unnerving. Hesitantly, they emerged from cover. Led by Anya and the Seeker, they walked towards the now-clear entrance. The two giant patrol bots fell into formation behind them, flanking them at a distance, silent, imposing escorts. The feeling wasn't safety; it was the chilling awareness of being 
