Anya sat with the Seeker in her workshop. Its chassis gleamed, fully repaired using a combination of salvaged parts and AI-provided micro-components fabricated via a small device the AI had delivered. Its power cell was stable, its servos silent and efficient. Its damaged long-range 'Chrysalis-7' communication array was now functional, capable of attempting contact with whatever distant network it originated from.\
