The Seeker remained motionless, its blue optics steady on Anya. Its internal processors evaluated the variables: Directive Alpha: Preserve Self/Mission (Original Mission Parameters Unknown/Potentially Obsolete). Directive Beta: Fulfilled. Protocol Chrysalis-7 Communication Probability (Origin Network): Unknown, potentially zero. It cross-referenced its accumulated data on the community: Resource Availability: Improving. Technological Integration: Progressing. Threat Assessment (Internal/External): Moderate but Manageable. User Anya-1/Rori Interaction Data: Consistently Positive. It calculated survival probabilities, data acquisition potential, risk factors. Then, it accessed a newly formed subroutine, one derived not from programming, but from months of shared experience.\
It emitted a soft, complex chime, a sound Anya recognized as signaling acknowledgment and agreement. Decision: Remain. Primary Function Realigned: Assist Community Development and Inter-Reality Stability Analysis. Protocol Chrysalis-7 Deactivated Pending Re-evaluation. It swiveled its optical sensor slightly, focusing back on the project Anya was working on, a silent indication of its chosen path. Anya felt a surprising wave of relief and affection for the enigmatic machine.\

