Tears welled instantly, blurring the image of the perfect little robot puppy. Not tears of sadness, but an overwhelming surge of pure, unexpected joy. This symbol \'96 this tangible echo of a lonely childhood dream, offered so freely, so thoughtfully, by the boy who had literally crossed realities to help her, who had 
